OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FToilet bungs and flood     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprevention to save homes   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Homeowners risk complacency, expense   
OL,6, and trauma unless they consider fitting
OL,7, simple flood protection measures, a new
OL,8, campaign will claim.                   
OL,10,FThe Environment Agency and others say  
OL,11,Fmillions of UK homes are at risk, and  
OL,12,Ffamilies can be forced out of a        
OL,13,Fflood-hit home for a year for it to dry
OL,14,Fout.                                   
OL,16,FThey say relatively cheap upgrades,    
OL,17,Fincluding toilet bungs and air brick   
OL,18,Fcovers, can help cut damage and costs. 
OL,20,FForecasters say flooding in the UK will
OL,21,Fbecome more intense and more frequent. 
